title: New photos show suspects’ car after Sacramento stabbing of French train hero
text:
Photo: Andrew Harnik, Associated Press In this Sept. 17, 2015 file photo, President Barack Obama speaks to Air Force Airman 1st Class Spencer Stone in the Oval Office of the White House in Washington. In this Sept. 17, 2015 file photo, President Barack Obama speaks to...
Sacramento police released new photos of the car believed to have been carrying the suspects who stabbed Spencer Stone, one of three men hailed as heroes for stopping a potentially deadly terror attack on a Paris-bound train in August.
